extends layout

block content
  main(role='main ')
    section#lab_video_slider
      .container-fluid
        .row.row-height
          .swiper-container
            .swiper-wrapper
              #slide_one.swiper-slide
                #lab_video_text_overlay
                  .container
                    h2(style="") Shifting the Paradigms of Tech in Nigeria 
                    p.masthead-para We believe that technology is core to any organization success in this age. We can help transform ideas into software product, right from the requirements elicitation to when the software is in use
                    a.btn.btn-default(href='/projects') View Our Work
                    a.btn.btn-warning(href='/aboutus') Learn About Us
                // end #lab_overlay
                video.slider-video(width='100%' preload='auto' loop='' autoplay='' style='visibility: visible; width: 100%;' poster='//dl.dropbox.com/s/ijyaav8qzkdtyt5/lab-coding-screenshot.jpg')
                  source(type='video/mp4' src='/images/lab-coding.mp4')
                  source(src='/images/lab-coding.mp4' type='video/mp4')
                  source(src='/images/lab-coding.webm' type='video/webm')
                  source(src='/images/lab-coding.ogg' type='video/ogg')
              #slide_two.swiper-slide
                #lab_video_text_overlay
                  .container
                    h2(style="") Our Team has the expertise to deliver the best in class software products
                    p.masthead-para We believe that technology is core to any organization success in this age. We can help transform ideas into software product, right from the requirements elicitation to when the software is in use
                    a.btn.btn-default(href='/projects') View Our Work
                    a.btn.btn-warning(href='/aboutus') Learn About Us
                // VIDEO
                video.slider-video(width='100%' preload='auto' loop='' autoplay='' style='visibility: visible; width: 100%;' poster='//dl.dropbox.com/s/5aeyg9ntj1fs8v1/typing-numbers.jpg')
                  source(src='/images/typing-numbers.mp4' type='video/mp4')
                  source(src='/images/typing-numbers.webm' type='video/webm')
                  source(src='/images/typing-numbers.ogv' type='video/ogg')
                // END VIDEO
      
    article#content-container.container-fluid
      section.search-section
    
        form.search-form.form-inline(action='/domain-search')
            input.ctrl-form( type='search', name='search_domain' autofocus='true'  placeholder='Claim that domain here')
            input.btn.btn-default(type='submit', value='find domain')
            <div id="results"></div>
      .container-fluid
        h2.home-h2 What are you tryin' to accomplish?
        .container-down-top.home-layout
          div.home-content  
            section.soft-dev
              .push-down-top-lg
                div.home-icons
                  img.home-icon(src='/images/webr.svg', title='Software development')
                |                         
                .text-left
                  h2 Software Dev
                  |                             
                  p Our software development shop employs time tested technologies and proven philosophy to deliver products that not only meets requirements, but that are also adaptible.
              div.home-content-btn
                a.read-more(href="software-development")
                  | learn more
              |  
            section.animation               
              .push-down-top-lg
                div.home-icons
                  img.home-icon(src='/images/ui-ux.svg', title='animation' alt="web animation")
                |  
                .text-left
                  h2 Web Animation
                  |                           
                  p Animation is the state of the art of the web. We deliver products from Virtual Reality website to animated E-brochure.
              div.home-content-btn
                a.read-more(href="web-animation")
                  | learn more
              |                         
                  
                    
            section.mobile                 
              .push-down-top-lg
                div.home-icons
                  img.home-icon(src='/images/mobiler.svg', title='mobile application development')
                |                         
                .text-left
                  h2 Mobile Dev
                  |                             
                  p We have mastered the technique of creating mobile applications for IOS, Android, and Windows App with Xamarin
              div.home-content-btn
                a.read-more(href="mobile")
                  | learn more
              |
            section.web-telephony 
              .push-down-top-lg
                div.home-icons                
                  img.home-icon(src='/images/talk.svg', alt='Telephony')
                |
                .text-left
                  h2 Internet Telephony                             
                  p  We create call center solutions for businesses, and help them reach a teeming audience via automated calls and SMS
              div.home-content-btn
                a.read-more(href="telephony")
                    | learn more
              |                 
    
    section#content-container2.container-fluid.section-3header
          div.jumbotron.container-fluid.jumbo-div      
            h2.home-section-h2 How would you like to accomplish it
            p.header-description we would shine the light on all facets of your company and reveal your domain model
          div.home-content.plain
            section.estimate
              div.main-lede
                h3 Click on the blue button to get started
                span.header-description Spare us some details about your project 
              div.main-action
                a.show.show-active(target='1' aria-hidden="true") Estimate
                  i(class="fa fa-chevron-down fa-1x pull-right" aria-hidden="true")
            section.nda
              div.main-lede
                h3 Start with an NDA
                span.header-description Do you have propriety information to share? Let's provide you with a non-disclosure aggrement(NDA)
              div.main-action
                a.show(target='2') Submit NDA 
                  i(class="fa fa-chevron-down fa-1x pull-right" aria-hidden="true")
            section.call
              div.main-lede
                h3 Schedule a meeting
                span.header-description We can provide you with 30 mintues of of our time on skype to discuss your next big thing
              div.main-action
                a.show(target='3' aria-hidden="true") Schedule
                  i(class="fa fa-chevron-down fa-1x pull-right" aria-hidden="true")


          section#section1.section
            h4 Write a brief
            .container-fluid
              .stepwizard
                .stepwizard-row.setup-panel
                  .stepwizard-step
                    a.btn.btn-primary.btn-circle(href='#step-1', type='button') 1
                    p Company details
                  .stepwizard-step
                    a.btn.btn-default.btn-circle.disabled(href='#step-2', type='button') 2
                    p Project details
                  .stepwizard-step
                    a.btn.btn-default.btn-circle.disabled(href='#step-3', type='button') 3
                    p Submission and feedback
              form(role='form' action="brief/add" method="post")
                #step-1.row.setup-content
                  .col-xs-9.col-md-8.col-lg-offset-2
                      h3  Company Details
                      .form-group
                        label(for="email") Email
                        input#firstName.form-control(name='email', type='email', required='', placeholder='Enter Email Address')
                      .form-group
                        label(for="brief") brief message
                        textarea.form-control(name="brief", cols="20", rows="6")
                      button.btn.btn-primary.nextBtn.pull-right(type='button') Next
                #step-2.row.setup-content
                  .col-xs-12.col-md-11
                      h3  Project Details
                      .form-group
                        label(for="companyName").control-label Company Name
                        input.form-control(type='text', required='required', name='companyName' placeholder='Enter Company Name')
                      .form-group
                        label.control-label(for='address') Company Address
                        input.form-control(type='text', name='address', required='required', placeholder='Enter Company Address')
                      
                      .form-group
                        label.control-label(for="phone") Phone Number
                        input.form-control( type='tel', required='required', name='phone' placeholder='Enter Company Name')                      

                      button.btn.btn-primary.nextBtn.pull-right(type='button') Next
                      
                #step-3.row.setup-content
                  .col-xs-12.col-md-11
                      h3  Step 3
                      .form-group                        
                        label.file
                        | Drop a file or click to select one
                        input(type='file', multiple='' name='nda' class='nda-input')
                        // use multiple, even if it’s not allowed, to be able to show an info text
                        p Take a moment to review the form, and edit any information.
                        button.btn.btn-success.pull-right(type='submit') Finish!

          #section2.section
            h3 Upload Your NDA here, we will sign it and send it back to you
            form.file-upload(method='post', action='nda/send', encType='multipart/form-data', ref='uploadForm' )
              label(for="name") Full Name
              input(type='text', value='Type your name here' name="name")
              label(for="email") Email
              input(type='email', value='provide your email' name="email")
              label.file
                | Drop a file or click to select one
                input(type='file', multiple='' name='nda' class='nda-input')
                // use multiple, even if it’s not allowed, to be able to show an info text
              button.pull-right.schedule-btn(type='submit') Upload
           
          section#section3.section
            h3 Book a schedule on skype
            
            form(action='/schedule/add', method='post')
              .header.row
              // row
              .row
                .inputs.contact.col-6
                  label(for='fullname') Full Name
                  br
                  input#fullname(type='text', name='fullname')
                .inputs.email.col-6
                  label(for='email') Email
                  <br/>
                  input(type='email', name='email', id='')
              // row
              // row
              .row
                .inputs.date.col-4
                  label(for='date') Date
                  <br/>
                  input(type='date', id='', name='date')
                .inputs.time-zone.col-4
                  label(for='timezone') Time Zone
                  <br/>
                  select.appt-sel(name='timezone')
                    option Timezone
                    option Lagos Central African Time
                    option London GMT
                    option Pacific
                    option Mountain
                    option Central
                    option Eastern
                    option Atlantic
                    option Chamarro
                    option Samoa
                    option Hawaii-Aleutian
                    option Alaska
              // row
              .row
                .inputs.contact.col-6
                  label(for='phone') Contact Number
                  <br/>
                  input#contactNumber(type='tel', name='phone')
                .inputs.email.col-6
                  label(for='skypeid') Skype ID (Email)
                  <br/>
                  input(type='text', id='', name='skypeid')
              // row

              .row
                .inputs.message.col-12
                  label(for='message') Message
                  <br/>
                  textarea.txt-appt(name='message')
              // row
              .row
                .col-12
                  button.schedule-btn.pull-right(type='submit')
                    strong Submit
              // row



    section.container-fluid.section-3header 
      div.jumbotron.container-fluid.jumbo-div
        h2.home-section-h2 Our work culture
      .container-fluid.culture-home
        .row.culture-pitch
          .container-fluid.culture
            h3.home-section-h3  Proven and Tested Technology Stacks
            img.culture-img(src="images/tech-stack.jpg", alt="technology stack")
            p The technology stacks we use have been tested and have been proven to deliver in their domain. Whether we are building a transformation pipeline, a client-facing web application, or a native cross-platform mobile application, we would deploy the best tools and platform in bringing the best experience to our clients. 
        //- p We are like pigeons, we stay with you through the ups and downs. We are fully committed to your project throughout the development lifecyle, event to the post production phase
        .row.culture-pitch
          .container-fluid.culture
            h3.home-section-h3 Proven and Tested Philosophy
            img.culture-img(src="images/agile-process.jpg", alt="Agile process")
            p We are disciplined in agile but we are not purists. Rather we rely on our discretion in replanning and reshifting our focus to ensure a smooth application lifecycle. Our low-level Agile framework is XP, so we enforce it within our developer sub-team. We leave teams to focus more on construction stuffs, We are more concerned about how the cross-functional teams work together on a project, so we embrace Scrum whole-heartedly. With us, your project would be in a stable state all the time.
        .row.culture-pitch
          .container-fluid.culture
            h3.home-section-h3 The client is king
            img.culture-img(src="images/client-king.gif", alt="Client is king")
            p In line with our Scrum mindset we not only bring the client as part of the project team, we are responsive to are clients and are interested in ways they would get the best return on their investment. This means we build with the business in mind as much as we want to listen to the needs of the client.
        .tech-img
          img.techs(src="images/html5.png" caption="HTML5")
          img.techs(src="images/reactjs.png")
          img.techs(src="images/net.png")
          img.techs(src="images/asp.png")
          img.techs(src="images/expressjs.jpg")
          img.techs(src="images/git.png")
          img.techs(src="images/jquery.png")
          img.techs(src="images/csharp.png")

    section.container-fluid
    script.
      var swiper = new Swiper('.swiper-container', {
      pagination: '.swiper-pagination',
      paginationClickable: true,
      nextButton: '.swiper-button-next',
      prevButton: '.swiper-button-prev',
      spaceBetween: 1,
      autoplay: 20000,
      autoplayDisableOnInteraction: false
      });


